BT 1 0 0 1 0 27 Tm 12 TL /F1 9 Tf 0 0 0 rg (The ) Tj /F2 9 Tf (singularity of consciousness) Tj /F1 9 Tf ( -- the gamma-) Tj (>) Tj (0 limit, pure awareness without content -- is not blocked by insufficient) Tj T* (cognitive effort. It is blocked by cognitive effort itself. The narrative is the wall. Every meditation tradition that has ever) Tj T* (existed converges on the instruction: stop the narrator. Physics now says why that works and quantifies the barrier.) Tj T* ET
